#: data/org.ayatana.indicator.notifications.gschema.xml:1
msgid "Discard notifications by application name"
msgstr "Abaikan notifikasi berdasarkan nama aplikasi"

#: data/org.ayatana.indicator.notifications.gschema.xml:2
msgid ""
"If an application name is in the filter list, all notifications matching the "
"application name will be discarded."
msgstr ""
"Jika nama aplikasi ada dalam daftar filter, semua notifikasi yang cocok "
"dengan nama aplikasi tersebut akan diabaikan."

#: data/org.ayatana.indicator.notifications.gschema.xml:3
msgid "Recent application names to suggest for the filter list"
msgstr "Nama aplikasi terbaru untuk disarankan ke daftar filter"

#: data/org.ayatana.indicator.notifications.gschema.xml:4
msgid ""
"Keeps track of recent application names so we can suggest them in the "
"settings."
msgstr "Menyimpan nama aplikasi terbaru agar dapat disarankan di pengaturan."

#: data/org.ayatana.indicator.notifications.gschema.xml:5
msgid "Enable do-not-disturb mode"
msgstr "Aktifkan mode jangan ganggu"

#: data/org.ayatana.indicator.notifications.gschema.xml:6
msgid ""
"On supported desktops enables do-not-disturb mode on the notification daemon."
msgstr ""
"Pada desktop yang didukung, mengaktifkan mode jangan ganggu pada daemon "
"notifikasi."

#: data/org.ayatana.indicator.notifications.gschema.xml:7
msgid "Maximum number of visible items"
msgstr "Jumlah maksimum item yang terlihat"

#: data/org.ayatana.indicator.notifications.gschema.xml:8
msgid ""
"The indicator will only display at most the number of notifications "
"indicated by this value."
msgstr ""
"Indikator hanya akan menampilkan paling banyak jumlah notifikasi yang "
"ditentukan oleh nilai ini."

#: src/service.c:221
msgid "from"
msgstr "dari"

#: src/service.c:270 src/service.c:300
msgid "Notifications"
msgstr "Notifikasi"

#: src/service.c:271
msgid "List of past system notifications, do-not-disturb switch"
msgstr "Daftar notifikasi sistem sebelumnya, sakelar jangan ganggu"

#: src/service.c:328
msgid "Clear"
msgstr "Bersihkan"

#: src/service.c:339
msgid "Do not disturb"
msgstr "Jangan ganggu"
